sub_title: Sunrock exec. / changing the energy system / net-zero carbon solutions for business & real estate / entrepreneur / scale-up builder
summary:
20 years experience including 15 years experience in the international energy sector which has brought me to unique places with great people.
10 years experience in the international renewable energy sector (the Netherlands, Germany, Middle East and the UK)  as COO, entrepreneur, project/business developer, investment manager and operations manager.
A healthy drive and passion for building successful businesses with over the years involvement in start-ups and scale-ups with some major and minor successes and one failure during the 2009 credit crisis. 
I was lucky to get on board of Sunrock in the beginning of 2018 when it was just underway to become one of the leading solar PV developers and asset owners in the Netherlands and now scaling up in Europe

I'm keen to connect with people who are interested to join one of our Sunrock teams; drive & passion is more important than experience .
And always willing to coach people so please contact me if there is anything I can do for you.
